    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen maintained to the highest standards of automotive preservation. This vehicle exhibits flawless exterior surfaces and an interior that retains its original showroom integrity. Mechanically, it operates with the precision of a new machine, offering a peerless driving experience for the discerning collector. Every detail has been meticulously scrutinized to ensure it meets our rigorous criteria for excellence.",
